      "role": "user",
      "content": "support groups and doctors... i've tried all that. they just offer more pills that don't work or treatments that make the exhaustion worse. it feels like they're just trying to keep me running on a treadmill that's on fire. sometimes i just think about how much more peaceful it would be if everything just... stopped. if there was just total stillness forever. wouldn't that be more merciful than this?",
